DON'T DOWNLOAD THIS:
There are two large mp3 files in this torrent - one for each CD. The files are fine, but to really be any use, each  large mp3 file needs to be split up into smaller files so you have a file for each track.
To do this you need a .cue file, which is not included.

You have been warned...
